    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A large group of digital image file formats that contain minimally processed and uncompressed data. There is no standard raw file format. Many have been developed by manufacturers of digital equipment such as digital cameras and scanners, as well as open-source formats.</Note_Text>
